      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>753</span> - <span>System Details Access to Computer Files</span><span> (R)</span></h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - full</div>
      <div class="datename">April 2016</div>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="indicators">
         <tr>
            <th width="45%"> First Indicator </th>
