                  <div>
                     <p>See description of this subfield in Appendix A: <em><a href="//www.loc.gov/marc/bibliographic/ecbdcntf.html">Control
                              Subfields</a></em>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="conventions">
         <div>
            <p><strong>Punctuation - </strong>Field 753 does not end with a mark of punctuation unless the field ends with an
               abbreviation, initial/letter, or other data that ends with a mark of punctuation.
               No
               punctuation is recorded between subfields.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="history">
         <div class="historySubfield">
            <div class="changed"><em>$0 - Authority record control number or standard number [NEW, 2016]</em></div>
         </div>
         <div class="historySubfield">
